<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 03:27:06 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>参议员称，美国电信遭受疑似与中国有关的黑客攻击，这是该国历史上最严重的一次</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/suspected-china-linked-hack-us-telecoms-worst-nations-history-senator-says-2024-11-22/</link><description>美国参议院情报委员会主席周四对《华盛顿邮报》表示，美国称与中国有关的电信公司遭受的黑客攻击是“我们国家历史上迄今为止最严重的电信黑客攻击”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 03:11:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/suspected-china-linked-hack-us-telecoms-worst-nations-history-senator-says-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示中美贸易和商业稳定发展有利于两国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-stable-trade-business-development-with-us-will-benefit-both-nations-2024-11-22/</link><description>中国商务部副部长王受文周五表示，中美贸易和商业事务稳定、可持续的发展趋势将使两国受益。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 02:46:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-stable-trade-business-development-with-us-will-benefit-both-nations-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>随着更广泛的战争风险上升，黄金飙升，欧元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-22/</link><description>由于俄罗斯降低了使用核武器的门槛并向乌克兰发射高超音速弹道导弹，黄金周五将创下近八个月来的最大单周涨幅，而欧元则徘徊在13个月低点。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 02:29:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统将访问图瓦卢、帕劳和马绍尔群岛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-visit-tuvalu-palau-marshall-islands-2024-11-22/</link><description>总统府周五表示，台湾总统赖清德将访问太平洋的图瓦卢、帕劳和马绍尔群岛。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 02:25:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-visit-tuvalu-palau-marshall-islands-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰战争加剧增加供应风险，油价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-rises-intensifying-ukraine-war-increases-supply-risk-2024-11-22/</link><description>俄罗斯称已向乌克兰发射弹道导弹并警告冲突扩大，增加了原油供应收紧的可能性，周五油价上涨。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 02:10:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-rises-intensifying-ukraine-war-increases-supply-risk-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统将访问太平洋盟友，但没有美国过境的详细信息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-visit-pacific-island-nation-allies-2024-11-22/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德办公室周五表示，台湾总统赖清德将于本月底开始访问台北在太平洋地区仅存的三个外交盟友，但政府拒绝透露美国过境地点的详细信息。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 00:11:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-visit-pacific-island-nation-allies-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>习近平访问摩洛哥并会见王储</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-visits-morocco-meets-with-crown-prince-says-state-media-2024-11-22/</link><description>据国家通讯社MAP报道，中国国家主席习近平周四对摩洛哥进行了短暂访问。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 00:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-visits-morocco-meets-with-crown-prince-says-state-media-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>随着贸易紧张局势加剧，中国企业寻求美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/corporate-china-seeks-dollars-trade-tensions-rise-2024-11-21/</link><description>由于贸易紧张局势可能会扰乱汇率，中国企业正在储备更多美元，以人民币定价合同，并开放进口额度，以减轻货币风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 23:06:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/corporate-china-seeks-dollars-trade-tensions-rise-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：韧性是游戏的名称，关注日本 CPI</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-11-21/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 21:52:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>国际原子能机构理事会通过伊朗决议，西方推动德黑兰进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/un-nuclear-watchdogs-35-nation-board-passes-resolution-against-iran-2024-11-21/</link><description>目的是迫使伊朗就对其核活动的新限制进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 21:01:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/un-nuclear-watchdogs-35-nation-board-passes-resolution-against-iran-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>政府称埃克森集团退出与圭亚那浅水石油区块的谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxon-mobil-pulls-out-talks-with-guyana-over-shallow-water-oil-block-gov-says-2024-11-21/</link><description>圭亚那副总统周四表示，美国石油巨头埃克森美孚及其合作伙伴已退出与圭亚那政府就勘探和开发浅水石油区块条款进行的谈判。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 20:28:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxon-mobil-pulls-out-talks-with-guyana-over-shallow-water-oil-block-gov-says-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>因安全担忧引发 FCC 提议对中国视频门铃制造商处以罚款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/fcc-proposes-fine-chinese-video-doorbell-manufacturer-after-security-concerns-2024-11-21/</link><description>美国联邦通信委员会周四提议对中国视频门铃制造商 Eken 处以近 735,000 美元的罚款，原因是其提供虚假信息并引发安全担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 16:51:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/fcc-proposes-fine-chinese-video-doorbell-manufacturer-after-security-concerns-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国指责美国对台政策导致防务领导人未会面</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-blames-us-policy-taiwan-defence-leaders-not-meeting-2024-11-21/</link><description>中国国防部指责美国对台湾的立场，导致中国国防部长本周在老挝举行的一次会议上没有与美国国防部长会面。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 14:22:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-blames-us-policy-taiwan-defence-leaders-not-meeting-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国声称“消灭”了缅甸北部的大型电信诈骗中心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-claims-wipe-out-large-telecom-fraud-centres-northern-myanmar-2024-11-21/</link><description>中国官方媒体周四报道称，中国和缅甸执法机构已“消灭”了在缅甸北部运营的所有大型电信诈骗中心，周末的一次行动逮捕了 700 多人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 13:06:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-claims-wipe-out-large-telecom-fraud-centres-northern-myanmar-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>香港民主活动人士黎智英否认在审判中煽动对中国的仇恨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-democracy-activist-jimmy-lai-denies-inciting-hatred-towards-china-2024-11-21/</link><description>民主活动人士黎智英周四在具有里程碑意义的国家安全审判中作证的第二天表示，他反对暴力，并没有通过呼吁抗议来捍卫基本权利来煽动对中国和香港当局的仇恨。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 12:24:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-democracy-activist-jimmy-lai-denies-inciting-hatred-towards-china-2024-11-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>